Grammy winner Wizkid has teased fans on his incoming album ‘More love, less ego’. The album is in collaboration with Alpha P and Wande Coal. He also expressed delight over reuniting with his friends. As his fans anticipate his next album, Big Wiz took to his Instagram story to share this update in three different posts respectively. Announcing one of the songs titled ‘madam’ he wrote : - Advertisement - NP: madam!   Popular skitmaker Isbae U faces alleged sex-for-skits…     Davido remembers late aide Obama DMW on posthumous 40th…     AY’s wife opens up on three miscarriages, anal bleeding   BIG Wiz/ @whoisalphap!! Prod @killertunes_tii !! MoreLoveLessego Album @djtunez love 4L “ Continuing he wrote: And that Big Wiz @wandecoal!! Da biggest shi*t” For the last post he wrote: “Feel really blessed Finishing this new project at home with friends surrounded with love”.